{"tid":1156201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"胡志偉鬧「八婆」　平機會：以貶詞攻擊女性身份　有違男女平等","createTime":"2019-05-15T12:42:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T07:35:51.000Z","uid":28195,"like":6,"dislike":410,"uniUserReply":108,"replies":[{"pid":"97ac2afee422b5e19d19a021afa46b5488005f0f","tid":1156201,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T12:42:34.000Z","msg":"立場報道2019/5/15 &mdash; 19:07<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/wu-01_R9mJz_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fwu-01_R9mJz_1200x0.png&h=304365e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>譴責胡志偉侮辱女性關注組</ins>、<ins>香港婦女聯盟</ins>、<ins>反黑金反港獨關注組</ins>等團體，昨日及今日分別到平機會請願，不滿胡志偉早前辱罵林鄭「八婆」的言論，並要求平機會跟進。平機會今日發新聞稿，指事件不屬於《性別歧視條例》的涵蓋範圍，平機會未能進一步跟進，亦未能處理相關投訴。<br />\n<br />\n平機會指，雖然其職權範圍未能處理有關投訴，但認為該言論並不恰當，既不禮貌，亦不尊重對方，並以貶詞攻擊特首女性身份，有違現今社會男女平等及兩性之間應互相尊重等核心價值，「平機會認為任何議會的討論必須以和平及互相尊重的方式進行，不應該使用不禮貌、不尊重、尤其針對女性或帶有貶意的詞彙」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%83%A1%E5%BF%97%E5%81%89%E9%AC%A7%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E5%85%AB%E5%A9%86-%E5%B9%B3%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83-%E4%BB%A5%E8%B2%B6%E8%A9%9E%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD-%E6%9C%89%E9%81%95%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3%E5%B9%B3%E7%AD%89/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%2583%25A1%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%2581%2589%25E9%25AC%25A7%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD-%25E5%2585%25AB%25E5%25A9%2586-%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%259C%2583-%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E8%25B2%25B6%25E8%25A9%259E%25E6%2594%25BB%25E6%2593%258A%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%2580%25A7%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BB%25BD-%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2581%2595%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E7%25AD%2589%2F&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2AbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=0a5686ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%2583%25A1%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%2581%2589%25E9%25AC%25A7%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD-%25E5%2585%25AB%25E5%25A9%2586-%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%259C%2583-%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E8%25B2%25B6%25E8%25A9%259E%25E6%2594%25BB%25E6%2593%258A%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%2580%25A7%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BB%25BD-%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2581%2595%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E7%25AD%2589%2F&h=2e756f04\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%83%A1%E5%BF%97%E5%81%89%E9%AC%A7%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E5%85%AB%E5%A9%86-%E5%B9%B3%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83-%E4%BB%A5%E8%B2%B6%E8%A9%9E%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD-%E6%9C%89%E9%81%95%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3%E5%B9%B3%E7%AD%89/</a>"},{"pid":"74f5a6546e3d91512ac00424f13b898b01203278","tid":1156201,"uid":53498,"like":697,"dislike":1,"score":696,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T12:45:03.000Z","msg":"八婆已經係讚緊佢,我叫開臭西"},{"pid":"b0e5f20f7149a1bb8de6270ea8257c46afc34162","tid":1156201,"uid":1790,"like":576,"dislike":3,"score":573,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T12:45:33.000Z","msg":"喂屌你平機會<br />\n功能組別同特首選舉有冇平等先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ac0eab81fd5a8cdb99366ec5680fd36e925f934","tid":1156201,"uid":21545,"like":149,"dislike":4,"score":145,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T12:45:47.000Z","msg":"女權膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55fa4991c566fd386690e2dccc7312059b86b019","tid":1156201,"uid":146257,"like":128,"dislike":0,"score":128,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T12:46:16.000Z","msg":"咁即係鬧佢垃圾就冇事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e36c209dbb0fc5b949a7666f7084967fa8cee2cd","tid":1156201,"uid":171192,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T12:46:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass